pull_request.title: Included picnic directly (vs. as cmake-built 3rd party lib).
pull_request.body:
Now uses OQS's rand; modified to avoid pedantic warnning; modified build and CI scripts (removed cmake dependency).

This not only simplifies OQS, but the downstream projects which won't need to deal with the picnic dependency.
